1836	 * Breakpoint: 720px. Above it, PublicHeader renders inline links and the
1837	 * founder-portal CTA; below it the same component hides those and exposes
1838	 * <MobileNavDrawer />. The article body bumps to 17–18px with looser
1839	 * paragraph spacing so reading at 360–414px feels comfortable rather than
1840	 * cramped. Hyphenation rules from the existing `.public-article-body`
1841	 * carry through; the rules below only widen `max-width` constraints and
1842	 * strengthen overflow protection for quotes / footnotes / pre blocks.
1843	 *
1844	 * Hero ASCII / heavy SVG: components live outside this stylesheet, but
1845	 * the breakpoint they should respect when shrinking-or-replacing on
